		<p>Proof-carrying code is a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cargo_cult_science" rel="nofollow">cargo-cult</a> scam.  See <a href="http://unqualified-reservations.blogspot.com/2007/08/whats-wrong-with-cs-research.html" rel="nofollow">here</a>.</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/?p=309&#038;replytocom=1401#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-1401", "1401", "respond", "309")'>Reply</a>		</div>
