		<p>I have responded (indirectly) to this post on Hacker News (<a href="http://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=2118149" rel="nofollow">response</a>, <a href="http://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=2119057" rel="nofollow">response</a>, <a href="http://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=2131870" rel="nofollow">response</a>).</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/?p=309&#038;replytocom=1392#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-1392", "1392", "respond", "309")'>Reply</a>		</div>
